    "explanation": "<p>Addition polymerization is the formation of polymers by addition of monomers without any loss of small molecules.</p>\n<p>Compounds with double bonds such as $\\mathrm{CH}_2=\\mathrm{CHCN}$, undergo addition polymerization.</p>",
